('acl_state7_red_cancel_line_confusing', 'STATE_7 red diagonal "cancel" slash across the 2πr ruler reads as confusing noise — remove it', 'MODERATE', 'peter_parker:renderer_primitives', 'The STATE_7 divide-by-2πr beat draws a red diagonal stroke striking through the 2πr ruler (drawAmperesStage, the ctx.moveTo/lineTo slash). The founder finds it unexplained and distracting ("please remove the red line, I don''t know why it is").', 'Do not draw a free-floating strike/cancel line whose meaning is not separately taught. Keep the isolate-B reveal (B = μ₀I/(2πr)) without a red slash; show the result compactly instead.', 'manual', 'STATE_7 shows no red diagonal line across the ruler; the isolate-B result still reads.', 'FIXED', ARRAY['amperes_circuital_law'], ARRAY['src/lib/renderers/field_3d_renderer.ts', 'src/lib/validators/visual/deriveStateMeta.ts', 'src/data/concepts/amperes_circuital_law.json'], 'session_2026-06-26_amperes_review2', 'incident'),
('acl_state78_explorer_needs_physical_rod_and_field_circles', 'STATE_7/8 show only the abstract 2D bar — must show the physical rod + current flow + concentric field circles + Amperian loop as the centerpiece, responding to sliders', 'MAJOR', 'peter_parker:renderer_primitives', 'The aclStageActive short-circuit blanket-hides the 3D acl_* scene (wire, current flow, concentric field circles, Amperian loop) on STATES 6/7/8 and renders only the 2D bar/ruler. For the result/explorer states this is too abstract — the founder wants the physical picture (a rod with current flowing, wrapped by field circles, an Amperian loop labelled I_enc) as the centerpiece, with sliding I showing current flow and raising r growing the loop/field radius; the 2πr bar and the formula should be small/aside.', 'In the result/explorer states show the physical 3D scene (rod + current flow + field circles + coaxial Amperian loop) as the centerpiece; bind I→current flow and r→loop/field radius; demote the bar/ruler to a small bottom strip and the formula to a corner. Never let the explorer be a static abstract diagram (Rule 24: picture over algebra).', 'manual', 'STATE_7/8 show the rod + current flow + concentric field circles + a coaxial Amperian loop centered; dragging r grows the loop/field radius and B dims 1/r; dragging I speeds/brightens the current flow; the bar/ruler is a small bottom strip and the formula is in a corner, with no occlusion.', 'FIXED', ARRAY['amperes_circuital_law'], ARRAY['src/lib/renderers/field_3d_renderer.ts', 'src/lib/validators/visual/deriveStateMeta.ts', 'src/data/concepts/amperes_circuital_law.json'], 'session_2026-06-26_amperes_review2', 'incident')
